From 92e1d69c20546c2d824b099a2ebf7452868f9cf0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 8 May 2025 15:13:04 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: cfg: remove DCCM offsets from new devices
Git-commit: 92e1d69c20546c2d824b099a2ebf7452868f9cf0
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

This is only used with old-style debug dump, which isn't
supported on newer devices, so remove the data.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250508121306.1277801-14-miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
